Running the Project

1. Set Up Apache and MySQL

Install XAMPP (for Apache & MySQL).

Start Apache & MySQL services.

Import the database schema into MySQL.



2. Deploy the Backend (PHP API)

Place PHP files in htdocs/employee_management/.

Access it via http://localhost/employee_management/get_employees.php.



3. Run the Cordova App

Install Cordova:

npm install -g cordova

Create a new Cordova project:

cordova create employeeApp
cd employeeApp

Add the web assets (index.html, script.js) inside www/.

Add an Android/iOS platform:

cordova platform add android

Build and run the app:

cordova build android
cordova run android
               
